{
  "description": "A close-up shot showcases a vibrant flax plant (harakeke) in full bloom. The focus is a tall, dark purple flower stalk reaching upwards, adorned with numerous, tightly closed, reddish-brown flower buds. At the very top of the stalk, the buds are starting to open, revealing hints of yellow and orange within. The base of the plant features long, arching green leaves, radiating outwards. Behind the flax plant, a dense, lush green hedge serves as a backdrop, creating a strong contrast in texture and color. The lighting is bright and natural, suggesting a sunny day. The composition emphasizes the plant\u2019s vertical growth and intricate flower structure.",
